original_title: The Judds: Love Is Alive - The Final Concert
overview: Follows Wynonna Judd along with her singing partners Ashley McBryde, Brandi Carlile, Kelsea Ballerini, Little Big Town and Martina McBride during the Judds tour. Also serving as tribute to the Judds' original swan song as a duo in 1991.
tagline: The Judds: Love Is Alive - The Final Concert
title: The Judds: Love Is Alive - The Final Concert
